title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update X USA - Santa Cathalina Island
description:
In this video we will have depart from Catalina Airport (KAVX) which is one of the handcrafted airports which has been added as part of World Update X. The airport is located on the island of Santa Catalina which is on the front of the west coast of the US. Besides the rocky parts of the island there is a small village including the Catalina Casino which is located in the Avalon Bay.
